---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css'; // Se hai un file CSS globale, importalo qui
---

<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pizzeria Da Mario | Vera Pizza Napoletana</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
      h1, h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
      body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
  </head>
  
  <body class="bg-stone-50 text-stone-900 m-0 p-0">
    <Header lang="it" />

    <main>
      <section class="relative h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
          <img 
            src="/immagini/pizza-hero.jpg" 
            alt="Pizza appena sfornata" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-[0.4]"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl">
          <span class="text-red-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Tradizione dal 1990</span>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
            La vera pizza cotta nel <span class="text-red-500">forno a legna</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-stone-200 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
            Un'esperienza autentica con oltre 170 posti a sedere nel cuore della città. 
            Ingredienti freschi, passione napoletana.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/it/prenota" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-red-900/20">
              Prenota un Tavolo
            </a>
            <a href="/it/menu" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/30 px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all">
              Scopri il Menu
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="py-20 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-stone-800">Ampie sale per ogni occasione</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Che sia una cena romantica o una grande festa di famiglia, il nostro locale offre **170 posti a sedere** suddivisi in sale accoglienti e climatizzate. 
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-stone-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-500">✔</span> Forno a legna tradizionale
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-500">✔</span> Ampio parcheggio gratuito
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-500">✔</span> Area bimbi e spazio eventi
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
            <img src="/immagini/interno-locale.jpg" alt="Interno della pizzeria" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-stone-900 text-stone-400 py-12 px-4 text-center">
      <p class="mb-4">© 2026 Pizzeria Da Mario - Tutti i diritti riservati</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Facebook</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>